OL,5,Cyears on
OL,7,FEach package contained food,
OL,8,Ftoiletries, and medical supplies to
OL,9,Fbolster islanders' diets who had to
OL,10,Fmake do with very little during the
OL,11,FGerman Occupation.
OL,13,FThey would have provided nearly 500
OL,14,Fextra daily calories per person.
OL,16,FAcross 2024, ITV Channel's Sophie
OL,17,FDulson interviewed five islanders who
OL,18,Frevisited their special memories of
OL,19,Freceiving their parcels.
