OL,4,CMichael Burke's SS Vega memories 80
OL,5,Cyears on
OL,7,FMichael Burke's story:
OL,9,FMichael was just a young boy when the
OL,10,FGermans came to occupy his home.
OL,12,FHe recalls the day they arrived in
OL,13,FJersey in the summer of 1940,
OL,14,Fexplaining: "We saw German planes
OL,15,Fcoming towards us - I remember two
OL,16,FGerman planes with the swastikas on
OL,17,Fthem flying over us.
