OL,3,C'We couldn't believe our luck':
OL,4,CMichael Burke's SS Vega memories 80
OL,5,Cyears on
OL,7,F"My father and I laid down on the sand
OL,8,Fand they flew over the top of us and
OL,9,Fwent over Mount Bingham and then
OL,10,Fbombed the harbour."
OL,12,FA few days later, the Germans landed
OL,13,Fat Jersey Airport and took over the
OL,14,Fisland for the next five years.
OL,16,FMichael recalls a time when he became
OL,17,Fsubject to the harsh Nazi regime,
OL,18,Frecounting: "One time a football
OL,19,Fbelonging to the Germans went past me
OL,20,Fand I didn't kick it back to them.
