OL,3,C'We couldn't believe our luck':
OL,4,CMichael Burke's SS Vega memories 80
OL,5,Cyears on
OL,7,F"A German soldier then came rushing
OL,8,Ftowards me and kicked me from behind
OL,9,Fand knocked me down and started
OL,10,Fkicking me, I got up and I had to run
OL,11,Fhome in a real mess.
OL,13,F"I went into the house and my father
OL,14,Fand mother were there.
OL,16,F"I told my father what had happened
OL,17,Fand my father couldn't do anything
OL,18,Fabout it."
