OL,3,C'We couldn't believe our luck':
OL,4,CMichael Burke's SS Vega memories 80
OL,5,Cyears on
OL,7,FSadly, it wasn't just the violence
OL,8,FMichael had to endure, but also the
OL,9,Fdeprivation of basic commodities like
OL,10,Ffood.
OL,12,FHe furthers: "The Germans who lived by
OL,13,Fthe Ommaroo Hotel used to put some of
OL,14,Ftheir garbage out and I can remember
OL,15,Fgoing in and looking through the
OL,16,Fgarbage.
OL,18,F"I remember finding loaves of bread
OL,19,Fthat were all mouldy and taking them
OL,20,Fback home - quite unbelievable really
OL,21,Fbut that's the way it was."
