OL,3,C'We couldn't believe our luck':
OL,4,CMichael Burke's SS Vega memories 80
OL,5,Cyears on
OL,7,FDespite having very little during the
OL,8,Fwar years, Michael's parents did what
OL,9,Fthey could to make sure he and his
OL,10,Fsister didn't go without.
OL,12,FHe explains: "My mother cooked up
OL,13,Fwhatever she could get for us but we
OL,14,Fdidn't know what we were going to get.
OL,16,F"My father started to collect rabbits
OL,17,Fto eat but I refused to eat the
OL,18,Frabbits - that was the best my father
OL,19,Fcould do.
