OL,3,C'We couldn't believe our luck':
OL,4,CMichael Burke's SS Vega memories 80
OL,5,Cyears on
OL,7,F"I think he used to go to work on the
OL,8,Ffarms and pick a few potatoes up but
OL,9,Fthen he would stick them down his
OL,10,Ftrouser leg so the Germans wouldn't
OL,11,Fknow that he was taking anything home
OL,12,Ffrom the farm - it really happened."
OL,14,FDuring the last year of Occupation,
OL,15,Fislanders became desperate.
OL,17,FFood was scarce and people had very
OL,18,Flittle to survive on, but when Michael
OL,19,Fwas 11, the SS Vega docked into
OL,20,FJersey's harbour on 30 December 1944,
OL,21,Fbringing precious food parcels.
