OL,3,C'We couldn't believe our luck':
OL,4,CMichael Burke's SS Vega memories 80
OL,5,Cyears on
OL,7,FMichael vividly remembers: "When the
OL,8,Ffirst ship came in, we went up to the
OL,9,Ftop of Mount Bingham and we saw the SS
OL,10,FVega coming in from Portugal, with the
OL,11,Fsupplies on board.
OL,13,F"It was unbelievable. We couldn't
OL,14,Fbelieve our luck because people were
OL,15,Factually close to starving at that
OL,16,Ftime, so without those Red Cross
OL,17,Fparcels, I don't know what would have
OL,18,Fhappened."
OL,20,FWhat did the Red Cross parcels contain?
